/blockquote><br />\n其實而家老麥買飛再等，分分鐘慢過kfc</blockquote><br />\nM記呢個問題之前討論過, M記而家用first order first service 呢個濕鳩系統, 前面果個如果一次買左3個餐, 後面等拎野食既人就食撚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本就係on9<br />\n仲有班廢物完全唔識multi task<br />\n例如前面有餐未出，後面有個新地筒，班友竟然係等前面個餐出完先去整新地筒</blockquote><br />\n我覺得應該係高層落order比所有分店, 一定要做晒先前既order先可以做下一個order</blockquote><br />\n其實係因為執野食個個好focus係第一張單<br />\n假設第1張單既食品未齊<br />\n就會執第2張單<br />\n用先落單先取餐既大前提"},{"pid":"815dca3650ab83cd072ac94b92e788860eceb58e","tid":303694,"uid":23706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"特色黎"},{"pid":"e1932533e9af2ae63f630390a3140861a7f9009c","tid":303694,"uid":4156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:50:17.000Z","msg":"新開果d 好撚快wor"},{"pid":"532daaa5ae299f19cd19a0a6782a54bc6833b9cf","tid":303694,"uid":106340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T11:54:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a154bcf38bbeac65ff9c31618f40b53967fe7d21","tid":303694,"uid":99438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:01:20.000Z","msg":"未試過唔使排隊，比m記踩住真係抵死"},{"pid":"3d88a58a9c6bfc96890a9c2ea0644db13ce37bff","tid":303694,"uid":25781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公司對員工好囉  慢慢做<br />\n做得快又係咁多錢</blockquote><br />\n對員工好就唔係收銀執貨一腳踢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da39e14625b911864f0fe157150d2d8ff56650e","tid":303694,"uid":6313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:16:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>緊係慢啦，叫幾百次巴辣雞粒都唔應機</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf55ec917f9da825e1575e132934bc36ae8199a","tid":303694,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T12:31:46.000Z","msg":"收最低工資咩都一腳踢 體諒下啦"},{"pid":"feae726f28b8d4109591dc1ddda37b3418ac899f","tid":30369